item.title: CVE-2020-11011|2024-08-04T11:21:14.259Z -- alanaktion -- phproject
item.description: In Phproject before version 1.7.8, there's a vulnerability which allows users with access to file uploads to execute arbitrary code. This is patched in version 1.7.8.
